# Linting & Formatting

## ESLint (Flat Config)
- **Config**: `eslint.config.mjs` (ESLint 9 Flat Config).
- **Import Sorting**: Handled by `eslint-plugin-perfectionist`. Do not manually sort imports.
- **Workflow**: Linting is mandatory. Fix linting errors manually before committing. No auto-fix on commit.

## Prettier
- **Config**: `.prettierrc`.
- **Workflow**: Format on save is enabled in Cursor.

## Common Linting Overrides
- `react/react-in-jsx-scope`: Off (Next.js handles this).
- `react/no-unescaped-entities`: Off (to allow apostrophes in text).
- `@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars`: Warn (with `_` ignore pattern).

## Import Order (Perfectionist)
Imports are automatically sorted in this order:
1. Types
2. Built-in (fs, path, etc.)
3. External (react, next, etc.)
4. Internal (@/*)
5. Parent/Sibling
6. Side-effects
